title: 114 Reflexive Arcade and Puzzle Games
description: The creative minds behind Jewel Quest return with a Solitaire game filled with riches and adventure! Play Tripeaks Solitaire in a new way using jewel-themed decks. Match card suits to earn pieces for the jewel board then turn the board&#039;s spaces to gold. Unearth buried cards, avoid cursed jewels and solve the 114 card layouts on a South American jungle trek. Experience 684 possible card scenarios through an exciting new Jewel Quest story. Embark on your card playing adventure in Jewel Quest Solitaire!
